pogList.notes: This is a magic secret door to the evil realm of NYM!

For the past few days, the city of Magnimar has been in the gripof terror. A murderer stalks the city’s streets in the gloamingpre-dawn hours, and each morning it seems a new and freshlymutilated victim appears in an alley. There have been four bodiesdiscovered to date—all worshipers of the goddess of healingand redemption, Sarenrae. The city guard desperately wants tocatch the murderer, yet he is a cagey and elusive foe. In orderto expedite the search, they have turned to you—known alliesof Magnimar and strong heroes of the people—to aid them instopping the culprit before he slays again.
